body:
"Figmachine  is a drum machine and 16-step sequencer built in Figma Make. 🥁 🎛️ 🎧 Four sounds, sixteen steps, and a row of lights let anyone start looping instantly. A single LO-FI toggle flips the whole beat into crunchy 8-bit grit, powered by a bitcrusher node. It’s a toy-like design with a real audio engine: sequencer, sampler, playhead, and effect. All created entirely with natural language prompts in Make. Quickstart:
- Press a step (1–16);
- Press a sound to add/remove;
- Press Play to loop;
- Adjust Tempo;
- Toggle LO-FI on/off;
- Clear all to reset. https://candy-tint-12219923.figma.s"

