"Mente Digital Pro 3.0 🧠🚀 Diseñé una experiencia interactiva que combina un Simulador de Decisiones Digitales con un sistema de XP y ranking por nivel de participación, transformando un simple quiz en una arena competitiva de pensamiento estratégico. Construido con Figma Make, integrando autenticación y lógica de base de datos para crear una experiencia más cercana a un producto real que a un prototipo. 🔗 Explora el proyecto aquí:  https://trunk-zippy-72122427.figma.site/  

🌐 Comunidad:  https://www.figma.com/community/file/1610571345041012030   #FigmaMakeathon

@Figma"

"Here's my entry (with a couple of hours to spare):
 Mood 🎨, the best of moodboard and bookmarking tools all in one collaborative platform for you to make your own. Store, create, collect, collaborate, connect... build moodboards that not only work, but also grow into your own mental library. The versatility of a whiteboard, with the power of organized bookmarks. Create your account and start using it here at  https://mood-app.figma.sites You can collect:
- Links;
- Notes;
- Images;
- Embed (YouTube, Spotify,...);
- Colors & color palettes;
- and Sketches

Built in less than 2 days with 214 pr"

"Mobile game design which based endless runner game inspired by the fast-paced urban chase mechanics popularized by retro classics.

Rush Run based endless runner built around different gesture controls (swipe to move, jump, and slide). The core objective is simple: survive longer, score higher, and unlock more.

Try it here;
 https://aloft-trio-72225011.figma.site  

